<example>

<title>
Image path rewriting example
</title>

<para>
If the <pragma>no_image_rewrite</pragma> pragma is
<emphasis>disabled</emphasis> and
<option>ImageDir</option> is set to "/standard/images", an image URL
like:

<programlisting><![CDATA[
<img src="fancy.gif">
]]></programlisting>

would be changed to:

<programlisting><![CDATA[
<img src="/standard/images/fancy.gif">
]]></programlisting>

With the directive enabled, the image URLs would be left intact.
</para>

</example>
